INSTALLING:
from the terminal, just type make and then return.

USAGE:
roots file

The file must be as follows:

N
ar_1 ai_1
...
ar_(N+1) ai_(N+1)

in the first line N is the highest degree of its monomials, 
the first number ar_j on the jth line is the real part and the second 
number ai_j the imaginary one.
